-------[Release Notez]--------------------------------------------------------

Dedication 4 is a mixtape by DJ Drama and Lil Wayne. The mixtape was originally 
supposed to be released on August 15, 2012, but got pushed several times and was 
released on September 3, 2012. It is the fourth installment of Lil Wayne's...
"Dedication" series, following its predecessors Dedication, Dedication 2 and Dedication 3.
It's also the fourth installment of Lil Wayne's "Gangsta Grillz" tetralogy...
